biography.placeOfBirth: Prague, Protectorate Bohemia and Moravia [now Czech Republic]
biography.bio: Jana Brejchová was born on January 20, 1940 in Prague, Protectorate Bohemia and Moravia. She is an actress and writer, known for Beauty in Trouble (2006), Courage for Every Day (1964) and In the Dust of the Stars (1976).
biography.name: Jana Brejchová

biography.bio: Tereza Brodská was born on May 7, 1968 in Prague, Czechoslovakia. She is an actress, known for Ulice (2005), Double Role (1999) and Díky za kazdé nové ráno (1994).
biography.name: Tereza Brodská

biography.bio: Jan Kacer was born on October 3, 1936 in Holice, Czechoslovakia. He is an actor and director, known for Smrt si rika Engelchen (1963), Valley of the Bees (1968) and Nobody Will Laugh (1965). He is married to Nina Divísková. They have three children.
biography.name: Jan Kacer

biography.bio: Jan Potmesil was born on March 31, 1966 in Prague, Czechoslovakia. He is an actor and writer, known for Bony a klid (1988), Proc? (1987) and Bolero (2004).
biography.name: Jan Potmesil

biography.bio: Marek Vasut was born on May 5, 1960 in Prague, Czechoslovakia. He is known for his work on Mission: Impossible (1996), Doktori z Pocátku (2013) and Blade II (2002).
biography.name: Marek Vasut

biography.bio: Zdenek Zák was born on June 9, 1952 in Prague, Czechoslovakia. He is an actor, known for Doktori z Pocátku (2013), Ordinace v ruzové zahrade 2 (2008) and Pojistovna stestí (2004).
biography.name: Zdenek Zák

biography.bio: Jirí Langmajer was born on June 3, 1966 in Plzen, Czechoslovakia. He is an actor, known for Ordinace v ruzové zahrade (2005), Ordinace v ruzové zahrade 2 (2008) and Le retour de l'idiot (1999).
biography.name: Jirí Langmajer

biography.bio: Jirí Pomeje was born on December 13, 1964 in Ceské Budejovice, Czechoslovakia. He is an actor and producer, known for Andelská tvár (2002), Muka obraznosti (1990) and Dotyky (1989). He has been married to Andrea Stastná since June 1, 2013. They have one child. He was previously married to Iveta Bartosová and Michaela Kuklová.
biography.name: Jirí Pomeje

biography.bio: Vlasta Meszarosová is an actress, known for Slunce, seno, jahody (1984), Who's That Soldier? (1988) and Slunce, seno a pár facek (1989).
biography.name: Vlasta Meszarosová

biography.bio: Anna Kreuzmannová is an actress, known for Oznamuje se laskam vasim (1989), Vlastne se nic nestalo (1989) and Príbeh '88 (1989).
biography.name: Anna Kreuzmannová

biography.bio: Ludmila Roubíková was born on January 4, 1919 in Vrchlabí, Czechoslovakia. She was an actress, known for Jako knize Rohan (1984), The Chintamani Carpet and a Swindler (1964) and My Brother Has a Cute Brother (1975). She died on August 11, 1991 in Prague, Czechoslovakia.
biography.name: Ludmila Roubíková

biography.bio: Lorna Vancurová is an actress, known for Vlastne se nic nestalo (1989), Nase deti (2001) and Ariadnina nit (1992).
biography.name: Lorna Vancurová

biography.bio: Václav Kotva was born on January 20, 1922 in Radnice, Czechoslovakia. He was an actor, known for L'incinérateur de cadavres (1969), Valley of the Bees (1968) and Shortcuts (1981). He died on November 3, 2004 in Prague, Czech Republic.
biography.name: Václav Kotva

biography.bio: Jirí Nemecek was born on May 5, 1923 in Praha, Czechoslovakia. He was an actor, known for Záhoranský hon (1968), Dny a noci (1953) and Velká filmová loupez (1986). He died on January 15, 1996 in Prague, Czech Republic.
biography.name: Jirí Nemecek

biography.placeOfBirth: Praha, Protectorate of Bohemia and Moravia
biography.bio: Karel Belohradský was born on November 17, 1943 in Praha, Protectorate of Bohemia and Moravia. He was an actor, known for Swing Kids (1993), Hart's War (2002) and Kafka (1991). He died on May 4, 2012 in Praha, Czech Republic.
biography.name: Karel Belohradský
